  "summaries": [
    "<b>Luminite</b> is a Hardmode ore dropped exclusively by the Moon Lord in stacks of 70–90 (<abbr class=\"expert\" title=\"Expert Mode\">90–110</abbr>). It can be used to craft Luminite Bars, which can then be used to craft several end-game items, like the Solar, Nebula, Vortex, and Stardust tools and armor.",
    "Crafting all items (excluding ammunition) requires a total of 317 Luminite Bars (1,268 Luminite; requires defeating the Moon Lord 15–19 / <abbr class=\"expert\" title=\"Expert Mode\">12–15</abbr> times). Crafting all items pertaining to one type of Lunar Fragment (i.e., armor, wings, pickaxe, and hamaxe) requires 68 Luminite Bars (204 Luminite) in addition to 85 of the Lunar Fragment; this requires defeating the Moon Lord only 3 / <abbr class=\"expert\" title=\"Expert Mode\">2-3</abbr> times."
